<header
  class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-ink px-6 py-28 text-paper sm:px-10 sm:py-32 lg:px-16"
>
  <picture class="absolute inset-0 -z-20 block h-full w-full">
    <source srcset="/images/hero-kali-cognitif.avif" type="image/avif" />
    <img
      src="/images/hero-kali-cognitif.jpg"
      alt=""
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
      loading="eager"
      fetchpriority="high"
      decoding="async"
    />
  </picture>
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-linear-to-b from-ink/95 via-ink/55 to-ink/95"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute left-1/2 top-1/3 -z-10 h-80 w-80 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-crimson/30 blur-3xl"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-7xl">
      <span class="text-crimson tracking-widest">KALI COGNITIF</span>
      <span
        class="mt-2 block text-2xl font-bold text-paper sm:text-3xl tracking-wide"
        >EN ENTREPRISE</span
      >
    </h1>

    <p class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg text-paper/85 sm:text-xl">
      Une nouvelle approche du sport en entreprise pour renforcer la confiance
      en soi, développer concentration, coordination (corps et mental), gestion
      du stress et cohésion d'équipe.
    </p>

    <p
      class="mt-6 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-crimson-light"
    >
      Maine-et-Loire &amp; Touraine — Angers, Saumur, Tours
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center sm:gap-5">
      <a
        href="#contact"
        class="mt-10 inline-block rounded-lg bg-crimson px-8 py-4 font-heading font-bold text-paper transition-colors hover:bg-crimson-light"
      >
        Organiser une session
      </a>
      <a
        href="/medias/Plaquette-Kali-Cognitif-Entreprise.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        class="mt-10 inline-block rounded-lg bg-crimson px-8 py-4 font-heading font-bold text-paper transition-colors hover:bg-crimson-light"
      >
        Téléchargez la plaquette
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
